snippet.textDisplay:
Heard this song a number of times while scrolling through Instagram reels and searched for it using the keyword "godilo"
Always thought this was a Telugu song or maybe a Tamil song but I was amazed to discover this was actually a Gujarati song
I thought I had adequate knowledge of Gujarati, watching TMKOC and Chup Chupke in my childhood days but how wrong I was 😅
Kudos to the creators and the platform!
Always thought Coke Studio Bharat has produced some brilliant songs but have failed to promote them like Coke Studio Pakistan, mainly due to the mammoth Bollywood industry and lack of A-list singers featuring on it. However this is exactly what this platform should be about. Don't feature established A-list performers, rather establish A-list performers
Once again kudos to the team! Cheers.
